This statement by Miroslav Kala, Vice-President of the Supreme Audit Office, is from an interview for the Aktuálně.cz website.
"The law will never be perfect, but it must be applied correctly, which, in my opinion, we lack," Kala commented on the current situation.
Such conclusions are provided by the joint inspection of the Czech and German control authorities.
